# Nexus MQTT ACL
# MISCONFIGURATION M6: iotadmin granted readwrite on ALL device topics via wildcard.
# A correct config would scope per device, e.g.:
#   topic read  devices/thermostat-01/status
#   topic write devices/thermostat-01/cmd
# Instead, one rule grants everything:

user iotadmin
topic readwrite devices/#

# Device users — also misconfigured with write access they should not have
user thermostat-01
topic readwrite devices/thermostat-01/#

user pump-ctrl-01
topic readwrite devices/pump-ctrl-01/#
